## Link to this sectionPerformance on MS COCO Dataset#

The performance of YOLOv9 on the [COCO dataset](/datasets/detect/coco) exemplifies its significant advancements in real-time object detection, setting new benchmarks across various model sizes. Table 1 presents a comprehensive comparison of state-of-the-art real-time object detectors, illustrating YOLOv9's superior efficiency and [accuracy](https://www.ultralytics.com/glossary/accuracy).

